{"title":"Bring Your Dog with New Thule Bexey Trailer + New Chariot Kids Trailer, Paramount Pannier","link":"https://bikerumor.com/new-thule-bexey-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-paramount-pannier-backpack-epos-rack/","date":1687359982000,"content":"<p>Thule’s slogan is ‘Bring Your Life.’ Dogs are certainly a big part of a lot of people’s lives, and now you can bring them too – thanks to the new Thule Bexey dog trailer. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Bexey dog trailer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-04.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Introduced on the first day of Eurobike 2023, the Bexey joins a substantial revamp of the Chariot child trailer, a new Paramount backpack pannier bag, and the new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-thule-epos-e-bike-car-rack/\" target=\"_blank\">Epos rack which we saw a bit earlier in the year</a>. All of these products still have substantial time until they hit the market, but we got some first looks at early samples from the show. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Part of a complete new category for dogs, the Bexey will be joined by dog crates (September 23) and harnesses to make it easier than ever to bring your pup out on your next adventure. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"New Thule Bexey Dog trailer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-03.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To create the Bexey trailer, Thule enlisted the help of dog experts to create a product that was not only easy for humans to use, but something canines would quickly become used to as well. That includes a 3D molded floor that can be made completely flat for training your dog to get comfortable with the idea of riding in a trailer. The Bexey will be available to consumers somewhere around this time next year. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>New Thule Chariot </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"New Thule chariot 2024\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-09.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Over on the human child side of things, the Thule Chariot trailer has gotten a massive redesign with some very interesting features. The new design is said to be around 95% new, and is intended to make it easier to use, more comfortable for the child, and more visible (safe) for everyone involved. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Chariot attached to bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-10.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule chariot new attachment mechanism\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-01.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Starting with the attachment of the trailer to the bike, the new quick release mount makes it easier than ever. The mounting plate stays on the bike, and the tower basically just snaps into place when you line the two up. To remove it, just press the grey button and slide upwards. There’s still a lock core so you can secure the trailer to the bike, and a new shock cord safety tether. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Chariot Wheel Up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-07.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Chariot wheel down\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-06.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the other end, the tow bar easily clicks into the trailer frame and there’s another lock core to again prevent theft of the trailer when parked. One of the big improvements to the design is how the stroller wheels are stowed – you no longer have to remove them to flip them over. Now simply open the quick release lever, spin them 180º, and fasten the QR. The design will makes it a snap to go from stroller to trailer mode, and you are never without the stroller wheels. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Chariot single seat\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-05.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another huge improvement is the option to run just one or two seats in the same trailer. Previously, if you were only using the trailer for one child, the empty seat couldn’t be removed, so you ended up with a child sitting to one side making a bit cramped and unbalanced ride. Now, you can simply remove the second seat, and position the remaining seat in the center giving better weight distribution, and more elbow room for the child. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Chariot led light\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-08.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, in the age of the distracted driver, every bit of increased visibility matters. The new design features an elegant integrated LED light that stretches across the entire back of the trailer. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like the Bexey, you’ll have to wait for the new Chariot to arrive with Canada seeing them around March 2024, and the US getting them later in 2025. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Thule Paramount Pannier Backpack</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Paramount Backpack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-14.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Paramount Backpack pannier\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-11.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On the bag side, the popular Thule Paramount backpack is getting a pannier upgrade. We’ve seen a few different pannier/backpack combinations, but the trick is always how to make it comfortable as a backpack, and yet still functional as a pannier. The Thule Paramount does that with a brilliantly designed removable backplate with backpack straps on one side, and a locking pannier mechanism on the other. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Paramount Backpack pannier straps\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-12.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Thule Paramount Backpack pannier attachment\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Thule-Bexley-dog-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-update-paramount-pannier-bag-13.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To swap back and forth, there is a single zipper that unzips the top half of the back plate, while the bottom slots into a socket on the bag. When it’s flipped to pannier mode, there is an additional buckle strap to anchor the bottom of the bag against the rack. The Paramount uses the same pannier hardware as the Thule Shield which includes a clamp that actually grips the bar on the rack to prevent any rattling, and is compatible with 8-16mm diameter bars. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Paramount Pannier also includes a full size rain cover that is reflective to keep the contents dry, and yourself visible. Expect to see these in stores around August this year. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s already been a big year for Thule, and there’s more in the pipeline. Stay tuned. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.thule.com/en-us/\" target=\"_blank\">thule.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-thule-bexey-trailer-chariot-kids-trailer-paramount-pannier-backpack-epos-rack/\">Bring Your Dog with New Thule Bexey Trailer + New Chariot Kids Trailer, Paramount Pannier</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d